# Edu Video Gen

Read **`docs/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`** for full architecture, API routes, file map, bugs fixed, and TODOs.

## Quick facts

- **Run:** `cd pkg && npm start` → `pkg/server/index.js`
- **Env:** `pkg/.env` (never commit)
- **Modes:** Short (6-scene one-click) | Long (Plan → Script → Media → Preview → Render)
- **Long-form testing:** `MAX_LONG_SUBTOPICS = 1` in `pkg/public/index.html`
- **Remotion:** pinned 4.0.484; components in `src/remotion/`; preview bundle `pkg/public/preview-player.js` (gitignored, rebuilt via `pkg/server/build-preview.js` on start)
- **Media:** uploads at `/uploads/`; `.mov` auto-transcodes to `.mp4`; HTML mockups use inline `ScrollingHtmlFrame`, not iframe
- **Preview vs render:** `timeline.js` caps preview durations (hook 8s, demo 16s, summary 18s); full render uses full narration
- **After changes:** restart server for backend; rebuild preview bundle after Remotion JSX changes

## Key paths

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| UI | `pkg/public/index.html` |
| Server | `pkg/server/*.js` |
| Remotion | `src/remotion/` |
| Assemble pipeline | `pkg/server/assemble.js` |
| Upload/transcode | `pkg/server/upload.js`, `transcode.js` |
